    {"type":"text","id":"webinar-text","x":570,"y":1650,"width":760,"height":380,"text":"🎯 LIVE WEBINAR — 90 MINUTES\nThursday 7:00 PM ET on Zoom\n\n0-5 min → Pre-Show (chat, energy)\n5-15 min → THE HOOK: Why 90% of marketing fails\n15-30 min → CASE STUDIES: $131K med spa,\n                    $516K dental, $38K aesthetics\n30-55 min → THE FRAMEWORK: 3 AI Systems\n55-70 min → THE STACK: $18,352 value → $997\n70-90 min → Q&A + CLOSE: Drop offer link","fontSize":18,"fontFamily":1,"textAlign":"center","verticalAlign":"middle","containerId":"webinar-box","originalText":"🎯 LIVE WEBINAR — 90 MINUTES\nThursday 7:00 PM ET on Zoom\n\n0-5 min → Pre-Show (chat, energy)\n5-15 min → THE HOOK: Why 90% of marketing fails\n15-30 min → CASE STUDIES: $131K med spa,\n                    $516K dental, $38K aesthetics\n30-55 min → THE FRAMEWORK: 3 AI Systems\n55-70 min → THE STACK: $18,352 value → $997\n70-90 min → Q&A + CLOSE: Drop offer link","autoResize":true,"lineHeight":1.25,"fillStyle":"solid","strokeWidth":2,"strokeStyle":"solid","roughness":0,"opacity":100,"strokeColor":"#1e1e1e","backgroundColor":"transparent","isDeleted":false,"angle":0,"seed":51,"groupIds":[],"frameId":null,"boundElements":null,"updated":1,"link":null,"locked":false},

