    {"type":"text","id":"offer-text","x":620,"y":2610,"width":660,"height":680,"text":"$997 OFFER — CHECKOUT PAGE\nhealthproceo.com/offer/pipeline\n\n72-HOUR CART: Thu 8:30 PM → Sun Midnight ET\n\n✅ Campaign Audit ($1,500)\n✅ 12-Module Masterclass ($997)\n✅ AI Blueprint ($1,500)\n✅ 10 Custom Ads ($1,500)\n✅ Skool Community 1yr ($2,364)\n✅ Weekly Webinars 1yr ($2,500)\n✅ Scaling Roadmap ($500)\n✅ 50+ Ad Swipes ($497)\n✅ Ops Templates ($997)\n✅ SPY + 253 Playbooks ($297)\n✅ 4 AI Playbooks ($1,200)\n🔥 BONUS: Audit Call ($500)\n🔥 BONUS: Slack 30d ($2,000)\n🔥 BONUS: DFY Campaign ($1,500)\n\nVALUE: $18,352 → PAY: $997 (or 3×$397)","fontSize":16,"fontFamily":1,"textAlign":"center","verticalAlign":"middle","containerId":"offer-box","originalText":"$997 OFFER — CHECKOUT PAGE\nhealthproceo.com/offer/pipeline\n\n72-HOUR CART: Thu 8:30 PM → Sun Midnight ET\n\n✅ Campaign Audit ($1,500)\n✅ 12-Module Masterclass ($997)\n✅ AI Blueprint ($1,500)\n✅ 10 Custom Ads ($1,500)\n✅ Skool Community 1yr ($2,364)\n✅ Weekly Webinars 1yr ($2,500)\n✅ Scaling Roadmap ($500)\n✅ 50+ Ad Swipes ($497)\n✅ Ops Templates ($997)\n✅ SPY + 253 Playbooks ($297)\n✅ 4 AI Playbooks ($1,200)\n🔥 BONUS: Audit Call ($500)\n🔥 BONUS: Slack 30d ($2,000)\n🔥 BONUS: DFY Campaign ($1,500)\n\nVALUE: $18,352 → PAY: $997 (or 3×$397)","autoResize":true,"lineHeight":1.25,"fillStyle":"solid","strokeWidth":2,"strokeStyle":"solid","roughness":0,"opacity":100,"strokeColor":"#1e1e1e","backgroundColor":"transparent","isDeleted":false,"angle":0,"seed":71,"groupIds":[],"frameId":null,"boundElements":null,"updated":1,"link":null,"locked":false},

